  "detailed_description": "Hexio is a relaxing, mind-bending, minimalist puzzle game that offers 96 meticulously designed levels to immerse yourself into. Connect all the nodes into beautiful and abstract shapes in this exciting puzzle game. A beautiful piano soundtrack accompanies you in your delightful experience. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615470/extras/f500a4f41ebb7e007837853fd6e86836.poster.avif?t=1630948352\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615470/extras/f500a4f41ebb7e007837853fd6e86836.webm?t=1630948352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615470/extras/f500a4f41ebb7e007837853fd6e86836.mp4?t=1630948352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Play</strong></h2><br>Each node must make a specific number of connections. Connect the nodes such that all of them have fulfilled that requirement.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br>★ 96 hand-crafted Puzzles<br>★ Clean and Minimalist Design<br>★ Hints available to help solve puzzles<br>★ Supports cloud saving<br>★ Optimized for human brains<br><br>Enjoy the Experience!",
  "about_the_game": "Hexio is a relaxing, mind-bending, minimalist puzzle game that offers 96 meticulously designed levels to immerse yourself into. Connect all the nodes into beautiful and abstract shapes in this exciting puzzle game. A beautiful piano soundtrack accompanies you in your delightful experience. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615470/extras/f500a4f41ebb7e007837853fd6e86836.poster.avif?t=1630948352\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615470/extras/f500a4f41ebb7e007837853fd6e86836.webm?t=1630948352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615470/extras/f500a4f41ebb7e007837853fd6e86836.mp4?t=1630948352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>How to Play</strong></h2><br>Each node must make a specific number of connections. Connect the nodes such that all of them have fulfilled that requirement.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br>★ 96 hand-crafted Puzzles<br>★ Clean and Minimalist Design<br>★ Hints available to help solve puzzles<br>★ Supports cloud saving<br>★ Optimized for human brains<br><br>Enjoy the Experience!",
